LOCUS       TOYEXONANCHOR            150 bp    DNA     linear   SYN 15-APR-2026
DEFINITION  Tiny synthetic exon-anchor teaching locus for GENtle shared-exon
            overlay dotplot exports.
ACCESSION   TOYEXONANCHOR
VERSION     TOYEXONANCHOR.1
KEYWORDS    synthetic construct; toy exon anchor; dotplot overlay.
SOURCE      synthetic DNA construct
  ORGANISM  synthetic DNA construct
            artificial sequences; vectors.
COMMENT     Hand-crafted documentation asset used to render a small
            shared-exon-anchor overlay dotplot. The sequence and transcript
            geometry are illustrative and intentionally tiny so the anchor
            semantics remain legible at a glance.
FEATURES             Location/Qualifiers
     source          1..150
